theorem Topology.interiorClosureInteriorClosure_eq_interiorClosure
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    interior (closure (interior (closure A))) = interior (closure A) := by
  apply Set.Subset.antisymm
  ·
    exact interior_mono (closure_mono (interior_subset (s := closure A)))
  ·
    have h : (interior (closure A) : Set X) ⊆ interior (closure (interior (closure A))) := by
      apply interior_maximal
      · exact subset_closure
      · exact isOpen_interior
    simpa using h
